text: Cﾄフﾄネina Ponor (; born 20 August 1987) is a Romanian artistic gymnast. She has won five medals at the Summer Olympics, three of them were gold medals. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:2004 Summer Olympics Category:2012 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic bronze medalists for Romania Category:Olympic gold medalists for Romania Category:Olympic silver medalists for Romania Category:Romanian gymnasts
